@startuml Data Flow Diagram

title Inventory Kamera - Data Flow from Game to GOOD JSON

skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA

' External Entities
rectangle "Genshin Impact\nGame Process" as Game #LightBlue
rectangle "GitHub Repository\n(DimbreathBot/AnimeGameData)" as GitHub #LightYellow
rectangle "User\n(Game Player)" as User #LightGreen
rectangle "Genshin Optimizer\n(Import Tool)" as Optimizer #LightCoral

' Data Stores
database "ScanProfile.json" as ScanProfile {
  note: Scan region coordinates\nResolution profiles\nSanctified shifts
}

database "datasources.json" as DataSource {
  note: GitHub repository URLs\nFallback sources\nEndpoints
}

database "inventorylists/\n*.json" as InventoryLists {
  note: Character names\nWeapon names\nArtifact sets\nMaterial names\nText hash mappings
}

database "GOOD JSON Export" as GOOD {
  note: genshinData_GOOD_*.json\nStandardized format\nImportable by optimizers
}

' Processes
rectangle "P1: Database Update" as P1 {
  process "1. Fetch Game Data" as P1_1
  process "2. Parse JSON" as P1_2
  process "3. Convert to GOOD" as P1_3
  process "4. Save to inventorylists" as P1_4

  P1_1 -> P1_2
  P1_2 -> P1_3
  P1_3 -> P1_4
}

rectangle "P2: Screen Capture" as P2 {
  process "1. Find Game Window" as P2_1
  process "2. Detect Resolution" as P2_2
  process "3. Select Scan Profile" as P2_3
  process "4. Capture Screenshot" as P2_4

  P2_1 -> P2_2
  P2_2 -> P2_3
  P2_3 -> P2_4
}

rectangle "P3: Image Processing" as P3 {
  process "1. Crop Regions" as P3_1
  process "2. Detect Sanctified" as P3_2
  process "3. Apply Adjustments" as P3_3
  process "4. Preprocess for OCR" as P3_4

  P3_1 -> P3_2
  P3_2 -> P3_3
  P3_3 -> P3_4
}

rectangle "P4: OCR Processing" as P4 {
  process "1. Borrow Engine" as P4_1
  process "2. Recognize Text" as P4_2
  process "3. Return Engine" as P4_3

  P4_1 -> P4_2
  P4_2 -> P4_3
}

rectangle "P5: Data Parsing" as P5 {
  process "1. Parse OCR Text" as P5_1
  process "2. Lookup Names" as P5_2
  process "3. Create Objects" as P5_3
  process "4. Validate" as P5_4

  P5_1 -> P5_2
  P5_2 -> P5_3
  P5_3 -> P5_4
}

rectangle "P6: Inventory Assembly" as P6 {
  process "1. Collect Items" as P6_1
  process "2. Match Equipment" as P6_2
  process "3. Build Inventory" as P6_3

  P6_1 -> P6_2
  P6_2 -> P6_3
}

rectangle "P7: GOOD Export" as P7 {
  process "1. Serialize to JSON" as P7_1
  process "2. Format GOOD" as P7_2
  process "3. Save File" as P7_3

  P7_1 -> P7_2
  P7_2 -> P7_3
}

' Data Flows
User --> P1 : "Update Database" (manual)
GitHub --> P1_1 : Game data JSON\n(characters, weapons, etc.)
DataSource --> P1_1 : Repository URLs
P1_4 --> InventoryLists : Parsed game data

User --> P2 : "Start Scan"
Game --> P2_1 : Window handle
Game --> P2_4 : Screenshot pixels
ScanProfile --> P2_3 : Region coordinates
P2_4 --> P3 : Raw screenshot (Bitmap/IImage)

P3_1 --> P3_1 : Read region coords from ScanProfile
ScanProfile --> P3_1 : Artifact regions
P3_2 --> P3_3 : Is sanctified?\n(purple detected)
ScanProfile --> P3_3 : Sanctified shift value
P3_4 --> P4 : Processed image regions

P4_2 --> P4_2 : Tesseract engine
P4_2 --> P5 : Raw OCR text\n("Cinder City Sands")

P5_2 --> InventoryLists : Lookup item names
InventoryLists --> P5_2 : Matched GOOD IDs
P5_4 --> P6 : Validated objects\n(Weapon, Artifact, etc.)

P6_1 --> P6_1 : Accumulate scanned items
P6_2 --> P6_2 : Match by EquippedCharacter field
P6_3 --> P7 : Complete Inventory object

P7_2 --> GOOD : GOOD v2 JSON
GOOD --> User : Download/save file
User --> Optimizer : Import GOOD JSON

' Error Flows
P2 ..> User : Error: Game not found
P4 ..> P5 : Timeout: Skip item
P5 ..> User : Error: Validation failed
P7 ..> User : Error: File save failed

' Notes
note bottom of P1
  **Database Update Flow:**
  - User initiates manually (optional)
  - Fetches from GitHub (fallback to alternatives)
  - Parses game data JSON (characters, weapons, etc.)
  - Converts IDs to GOOD format
  - Saves to local inventorylists/*.json
  - Defensive checks: Skip unreleased content

  **Update Frequency:**
  - After major game updates (6.4, 6.5, etc.)
  - When new characters/weapons released
  - If data repository URL changes
end note

note bottom of P3
  **Image Processing Flow:**
  1. Crop regions from full screenshot
     - Uses ScanProfile coordinates
     - Different profiles for 16:9, 16:10, Steam Deck
  2. Detect sanctified artifact (purple bar)
     - Color range check: B>R>=G, B>150
     - Handles light and dark purple variants
  3. Apply coordinate adjustments if sanctified
     - Add sanctifyShift to Y-coordinates
     - 16:9: +0.0520, 16:10: +0.0471
  4. Preprocess for OCR
     - Grayscale, contrast enhancement
     - Noise reduction
end note

note bottom of P4
  **OCR Engine Pool:**
  - 8 pre-initialized Tesseract engines
  - ConcurrentBag for thread-safe access
  - Workers borrow/return engines
  - Custom trained data: genshin_best_eng.traineddata

  **Timeout Handling:**
  - 30-second timeout per OCR task
  - If timeout: Skip item, log error, continue
  - Prevents application freeze
end note

note bottom of P5
  **Data Parsing Flow:**
  1. Parse OCR text
     - Regex patterns for stats (e.g., "ATK% +46.6%")
     - Split substats by line breaks
  2. Lookup names in inventorylists
     - Match character names (handle Traveler/Wanderer)
     - Match weapon/artifact names
     - Use text hash if available
  3. Create game objects
     - Weapon(name, level, refinement, rarity)
     - Artifact(set, slot, mainStat, subStats, level, rarity)
  4. Validate
     - Check required fields populated
     - Verify stat values in valid ranges
     - Log errors if validation fails
end note

note bottom of P6
  **Inventory Assembly:**
  1. Collect all scanned items
     - Weapons, Artifacts, Characters, Materials
     - Accumulated during scan process
  2. Match equipped items to characters
     - Use EquippedCharacter field from OCR
     - Match by character GOOD name
     - Assign to character.Weapon, character.Artifacts[]
  3. Build final Inventory object
     - Inventory { Weapons, Artifacts, Materials }
     - Characters with equipped items
     - Ready for GOOD export
end note

note bottom of P7
  **GOOD Export Format:**
  {
    "format": "GOOD",
    "version": 2,
    "source": "Inventory Kamera",
    "characters": [
      {
        "key": "HuTao",
        "level": 90,
        "constellation": 1,
        "ascension": 6,
        "talent": { "auto": 10, "skill": 10, "burst": 9 }
      }
    ],
    "weapons": [
      {
        "key": "StaffOfHoma",
        "level": 90,
        "ascension": 6,
        "refinement": 1,
        "location": "HuTao",
        "lock": true
      }
    ],
    "artifacts": [ ... ]
  }
end note

@enduml
